title: Baked Spaghetti Squash with Feta
ingredients: ['1 spaghetti squash, halved lengthwise and seeded', '2 tablespoons olive oil', '1 onion, chopped', '1 clove garlic, minced', '280g (10 oz) chopped tomatoes', '110g (4 oz) feta, crumbled', '3 tablespoons sliced black olives', '2 tablespoons chopped fresh basil']
